    "description": {
      "value": "<div><p>You unleash a string of insults laced with subtle enchantments at a creature you can see within range. If the target can hear you (though it need not understand you), it must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or take [[/r 1d4]] psychic damage and have disadvantage on the next attack roll it makes before the end of its next turn.</p></div><div><div><p>The spell causes disadvantage on the next 2 attacks when you reach 5th level and deals an additional d4 damage ([[/r 2d4]]), the next 3 attacks at 11th level and deals an additional d4 damage ([[/r 3d4]]), and the next 4 attacks at 17th level and deals an additional d4 damage ([[/r 4d4]]).</p></div></div>",
